Overview 
========

RPA program runs in three modes so far. The input file is rpa_kpm.ini
1)  eig_min  
2)  eig_all
3)  kpm

eig_min: compute the lowest eigenvalue of sqrt(vc)\chi_{KS}sqrt(vc)
eig_all:  compute N lowest eigenvalues of sqrt(vc)\chi_{KS}sqrt(vc)
kpm:      do the KPM sampling



Description of the scripts
==========================

get_eigen_min_two_systems.py: 
Obtain the lowest eigenvalues of sqrt(vc)\chi_{KS}sqrt(vc) of system 1 and system 2
   
get_exact_ERPA.py: 
Obtain the N lowest eigenvalues of sqrt(vc)\chi_{KS}sqrt(vc) of system 1 and system 2, and compute RPA energy.
   
